        "# This Week's Progress\n",
        "\n",
        "Brief narrative of what was accomplished.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Tasks Completed\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Created Template\n",
        "2. Cleaned and Standardized SF adresses\n",
        "3. Use Census Geocoder to geocode addresses\n",
        "\n",
